\FF[himawari_kamen]Himawari: "Seriously... You're useless. Weren't you the one

\F[beni_kamenoti2]\FF[himawari_kamen]\AA[1]Akane: "I never boasted... But finding a place where 10

\F[beni_kamenoti2]\FF[inu_kamen1]\AA[2]Maple: "That being said, I had an idea. With this number of
